Decorator to read all the lines in the .ini file first before running a certain function

All the file lines will be saved in {attr}`IniFile._fileLines`

# Examples

```{code-block} python
:linenos: true

@_readLines
def printLines(self):
    for line in self._fileLines:
        print(f"LINE: {line}")
```

